Revision history for Dist-Zilla-PluginBundle-FLORA

0.18  Sun 30 Jul 2023 14:44:19 PDT
  * removed [Test::NewVersion], which has fallen into disrepair

0.17  Tue  2 Feb 2016 18:47:59 PST
  * re-release using latest version of self, to eliminate UNKNOWN results from
    cpantesters

0.16  Sat  1 Aug 2015 13:30:13 PDT
  * added [Test::NewVersion], to guard against not bumping the distribution
    version
  * added [MinimumPerl], for metadata, and [Test::ReportPrereqs], to ensure
    there will always be a runnable test for every distribution
  * added missing prereqs (RT#106167)

0.15  Fri  3 Jul 2015 13:10:37 PDT
  * resolve deprecation warnings from old plugins
  * add ConfigSlicer, PluginRemover roles

0.14  Tue, 05 Jul 2011 23:51:47 +0200
  * Use metacpan.org instead of search.cpan.org for the distribution homepage
    metadata.

0.13  Tue, 05 Oct 2010 00:24:29 +0200
  * Allow 'catsvn' to be used to refer to dists in Catalyst's SVN repository.
  * Use AutoPrereqs instead of the deprecated AutoPrereq plugin.
  * Minor documentation fixes.

0.12  Tue, 15 Jun 2010 11:44:01 +0200
  * Fix gitmo repository urls.

0.11  Sat, 05 Jun 2010 20:18:39 +0200
  * Allow EOLTests trailing whitespace checks to be turned off.
  * Depend on a Pod::Weaver::PluginBundle::FLORA using
    Pod::Weaver::Plugin::Encoding.

0.10  Sat, 29 May 2010 17:06:50 +0200
  * Use NoTabsTests and EOLTests instead of SanityTests.

0.09  Wed, 26 May 2010 04:07:04 +0200
  * Emit additional resources metadata for CPAN META 2.0.

0.08  Sun, 23 May 2010 22:52:39 +0200
  * Add a way to disable pod coverage testing.

0.07  Thu, 20 May 2010 23:07:15 +0200
  * Depend on Pod::Weaver::PluginBundle::FLORA 0.02 for the TYPE collector
    section.

0.06  Sat, 15 May 2010 13:07:27 +0200
  * Make specifying github repo urls with camel case dist names easier.
  * Allow specifying the github username to use.
  * Enable the SanityTests plugin.

0.05  Sun, 09 May 2010 23:23:19 +0200
  * Make authority configurable.

0.04  Sat, 08 May 2010 21:22:38 +0200
  * Re-enable PkgVersion.

0.03  Sat, 08 May 2010 21:13:24 +0200
  * Use @Basic and add Pod{Syntax,Coverage}Tests instead of using @Classic and
    removing {Pod,Bump}Version.

0.02  Fri, 07 May 2010 04:13:13 +0200
  * Set authority to cpan:FLORA in both the modules and and metadata.

0.01  Thu, 06 May 2010 20:20:29 +0200
  * Initial release.
